description._content: Description: Melalap - Keningau Road. 7. The 'rock wall' farther on, with natives working on cutting through the end of the 'tanjong' (spur). Location: Borneo Date: 1929 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Melalap - Keningau Road. 8. The 'rock wall', a view of it from the Keningau side. Location: Borneo Date: 1929 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Melalap - Keningau Road. 9. An improvised drag (fitted with 8 inch wide 'merabau' wooden wheels) harnessed to a Buffalo for removing earth. It will take a load of 20 baskets (nearly 1/2 ton) a time. Location: Borneo Date: 1929 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Melalap - Keningau Road. 10. Location: Borneo Date: 1929 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Melalap - Keningau Road. 11. The same at N.end, and looking down on the earth work under construction towards Surveyor Grant's bridge site over Mesalog R. Location: Borneo Date: 1929 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Melalap - Keningau Road. 12. Small partially completed fill between 'neck' and the Mesalog River. Location: Borneo Date: 1929 ------------------------------------------------------ Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/517.
